This is a extentions to support a mailservice workload for rain.

To use this extension, 
You also need an functional mailservice with POP3 and SMTP support.

To do mailservice benchmarks with this extension use the executable jar file, contained in this repository "rain_benchmark_mailworkload.jar".

Adapt the configuration files of this extension located in "config/" to you needs.

To run a benchmark: 
java -Xmx1g -Xms512m -jar rain_benchmark_mailworkload.jar config/rain.config.mailapp.json